Yeah, room service.

844
01:03:14,212 --> 01:03:16,646
<i>Excuse me?
Honey, we don't do room service.</i>

845
01:03:16,747 --> 01:03:18,407
What do you mean,
you don't do room service?

846
01:03:18,515 --> 01:03:20,881
<i>I mean, we don't do room service.</i>

